query:
SELECT id, householdId, name, assignedTo, JSON_TYPE(assignedTo) as jsonType
FROM tasks 
WHERE assignedTo IS NOT NULL 
AND JSON_TYPE(assignedTo) != 'ARRAY'
LIMIT 10
